message.body: Any of the job postings I sent helpful?
Mm. Not really. I didn't see any nursing ones that apply to me. Most we're more medical, not nursing. But thanks though. I appreciate it. I'm looking int
o a hostess position at Postitano coast. My friend Jessica works there now and is leaving.

Maybe. But you probably have to have experience for a barista. Haha. Can you send it to me if you see it again?
